Privacy Policy for BrightAI

Last Updated: November 17, 2023

1. Introduction
Welcome to BrightAI! We are committed to protecting your privacy and ensuring you have a positive experience on our app. This Privacy Policy outlines our practices regarding the collection, use, and disclosure of your information.

2. Information Collection
a. Personal Information: We may collect personal information such as your name, email address, and other contact details when you register for our app.
b. Usage Data: Information on how you use the app, including your browsing history, preferences, and interactions with the AI features.
c. Image Data: Any images you upload for generation or processing.

3. Use of Information
Your information is used to:

Provide, maintain, and improve our services.
Communicate with you about updates, support, and administrative messages.
Enhance AI algorithms and app functionality.
4. Sharing of Information
We do not sell your personal information. Information may be shared with third-party service providers only to support our app's functionality, under strict privacy terms.

5. Data Security
We implement robust security measures to protect your data from unauthorized access, alteration, disclosure, or destruction.

6. Children's Privacy
BrightAI is not intended for use by children under the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children under 13.

7. Changes to This Privacy Policy
We may update this policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new Privacy Policy on this page.

8. Contact Us
If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at [Your Contact Information].
